         <xocs:funding-text>Funding: This work was supported by the Ministry of the Environment [Dnro YM 57/5512/2015 , to AP and HB]; and by The Strategic Research Council at the Academy of Finland via the IBC-Carbon project [grant number 312559 , to RH and RV]. </xocs:funding-text>
         <xocs:funding-text>We thank Linda Kartano for processing the modelled data in ArcGIS. We are grateful to Bea Maas and two reviewers for their constructive comments that greatly improved the original version of the manuscript. University of Jyv\u00E4skyl\u00E4, Finnish Environment Institute and the Finnish Museum of Natural History Luomus at the University of Helsinki are acknowledged for the working environment. We acknowledge funding from the Ministry of the Environment to the Finnish forest raptor project (part of the METSO-programme) and from the Academy of Finland to the IBC-Carbon project. </xocs:funding-text>
